The paper proposes a new embedding method for efficient classification and regression of functions of single vectors, approximation of distance functions, and non-Euclidean, semimetric learning. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
